<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>234</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hi vawlei cu sual mui lakah a tlau cang, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!
 Chun niceu bang Amah lianhnak kha a tlang, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[C1]
   Nannih vialte ceunak ah ra u, Muihnak chungin ceunak a chuak cang,
   Mitcaw mi nih khua kan hmuh khawh cang, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[V2]
 Jesuh hngatchanmi ca khuamui a um lo, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si! Lam
 hmuhsaktu zulmi nih ceunak an hmuh, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[C2]
   Nannih vialte ceunak ah ra u, Muihnak chungin ceunak a chuak cang,
   Mitcaw mi nih khua kan hmuh khawh cang, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[V3]
 Sualnak in mitcaw, mui lak aa chokmi hna, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si! An
 fial bang i tawl law ceunak an hmuh lai, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[C3]
   Nannih vialte ceunak ah ra u, Muihnak chungin ceunak a chuak cang,
   Mitcaw mi nih khua kan hmuh khawh cang, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[V4]
 Vancung khua ah ni ceunak a herh ti lo, Khi khua ceunak Jesuh a si;
 Sui khuali-pi ceunak cu Tuufa a si, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!

[C4]
   Nannih vialte ceunak ah ra u, Muihnak chungin ceunak a chuak cang,
   Mitcaw mi nih khua kan hmuh khawh cang, Vawlei ceunak Jesuh a si!</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>VAWLEI CEUNAK CU JESUH A SI CH234</title>
</song>